        "element": "span",
        "class": "cverse2",
        "text": "Now, thou son of man, wilt thou {a} judge, wilt thou judge the bloody city? yea, thou shalt show her all her abominations.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Now, thou son of man, wilt thou ",
